  "texts": [
    "The results for 1, 3, and 5-shot experiments of GPT-3.5 are shown in Table 3.",
    "We limit these experiments to the 1, 3, and 5-shot setting to maintain a high degree of semantic similarity between the examples the target question.",
    "While it would be technically possible to use more shots, this could introduce irrelevant information that could hinder the model's ability to learn the concepts relevant to the target question.",
    "https://huggingface.co/sentence-transformers/all-MiniLM-L -v Table 3 shows that similarity-based few shot prompting performs 4% worse than random few-shot prompting shown previously in Table 2.",
    "There are several potential explanations for this drop in accuracy."
